
            Functions supported by [XBBS] 2.3

     A >> Re-scan for Msgs. E >> Enter a message
     K >> Read bulletin     R >> Retrieve a message
     K >> Kill a message    I >> Re-type information
     S >> Message headings  X >> Expert user mode
     C >> Exit to CP/M      G >> Exit system (Hang up)

     In the R mode all messages above your entry number,
     will be shown 1 at a time; followed by a command
     prompt. Help menu is available. Multiple retreival
     of known message numbers?   Yes!!

     Example>> From main command line only!
               R;1;5;7;9;10 will retreive those numbers.
     To advance to next pre-selected number just enter 
